data.description: Take a look at this incredible 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that is only 2 years old. Its beautiful and very well maintained with many modernizations and upgrades. In the front of the house, you will find three secondary bedrooms, a secondary bathroom, and a spacious laundry room. The entry hallway leads to a open living room and kitchen which showcases 36-in. upper kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom show-offs a large walk-in closet and a master bath containing an extended walk-in shower with tile surrounding, an extended dual sink vanity, and a towel closet. This home is ready for its new owners, plus the outdoor space is fully fenced and great for entertainment and family time. Don't miss the opportunity to own this dream home!
